Work.Title: StartEase
Work.Description: The startup ecosystem in Algeria is on the rise. The Ministry of Higher Education and Scientific Reasearch introduces 'a diploma-a startup/a diploma-a patent' program which aims to direct students towards university project incubators and techological platforms, where there can work on projects ans potentially be accepted as startups. However, the lack of a centralized a,d efficient platform for traking and managing these projects creates difficulties for students; academic institutions and incubators in managing these projects effectively.</br>Here comes the role of our platform StartEase. It aims to address these inssues by providing a comprehensive solution that enables efficient tracking and management of end-of-studies projects related to 'a diploma-a startup/a diploma-a patent' in Algerian educational institutions.

Work.Title: Paradise Perfume
Work.Description: A Mobile App that serves the purpose of managing orders and loyalty cards for a local perfume store, this app provides various functionalities for the clients going from placing multiple orders, making pre-ordres and consulting the loyalty card. The store owner has the ability to manage the list of perfumes, see stats on the store's sales, consult and manage orders from client and other useful functionalities.

Work.Title: E-Sbitar
Work.Description: Healthcare service system is proposed to address the increasing demand for healthcare services in the modern world. With the advent of information and communication technology, it has become imperative to leverage this technology to improve the quality and accessibility of healthcare services. The E-Sbitar system aims to provide instant medical assistance to individuals in need by leveraging the power of technology. This Software Requirements Specification document aims to provide a detailed overview of the requirements for the development and implementation of the E-Sbitar system. It outlines the functional and non-functional requirements that the system must fulfill to ensure its successful implementation and usage. This document serves as a reference for the development team, stakeholders, and end-users, providing a clear understanding of the system's features and capabilities.

Work.Title: Stacker
Work.Description: during my daily activities, I encounter so many things which I want to look them up, but even if I note them somewhere, I always end up forgetting about the most of them, this was the motive for this simple web app, whenenver I want I can Stack a topic, along with how much time I want to spend on this topic, and whenenver I have free time, I tell Stacker and it will pick a topic from my stack .
